OL,7,FFather Ted co-creator Graham Linehan
OL,8,Fhas been cleared of harassing a
OL,9,Ftransgender activist on social media
OL,10,Fbut found guilty of criminal damage to
OL,11,Ftheir mobile phone outside a
OL,12,Fconference in London last year.
OL,14,FThe 57-year-old flew in from Arizona
OL,15,Fto appear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt in person on Tuesday, where
OL,17,Fjudgment was delivered by District
OL,18,FJudge Briony Clarke.
