OL,7,FLinehan denied harassing Sonia Brooks
OL,8,Fon social media between October 11 and
OL,9,FOctober 27 last year, and a charge of
OL,10,Fcriminal damage to their mobile phone
OL,11,Fon October 19 last year outside the
OL,12,FBattle of Ideas conference in
OL,13,FWestminster.
OL,15,FReading a summary of her judgment, the
OL,16,Fjudge said she was not satisfied that
OL,17,FLinehan's conduct amounted to
OL,18,Fharassment or that the complainant was
OL,19,Fas distressed as they made themselves
OL,20,Fout to be.
