OL,7,FShe said that Linehan had not tagged
OL,8,Fthe activist in his social media
OL,9,Fposts, bar one, and that while his
OL,10,Fcomments were "deeply unpleasant,
OL,11,Finsulting and even unnecessary," they
OL,12,Fwere not "oppressive or unacceptable
OL,13,Fbeyond merely unattractive, annoying
OL,14,For irritating."
OL,16,FThe judge found Linehan had taken
OL,17,FBrooks' phone because he was "angry
OL,18,Fand fed up", and had damaged it by
OL,19,Fknocking it to the ground.
