OL,7,FThe trial heard that Brooks had begun
OL,8,Ftaking photographs of delegates at the
OL,9,Fevent during a speech by Fiona
OL,10,FMcAnena, director of campaigns at Sex
OL,11,FMatters.
OL,13,FOutside the event, the activist asked
OL,14,FLinehan: "Why do you think it is
OL,15,Facceptable to call teenagers domestic
OL,16,Fterrorists?"
