OL,7,FIn response, the court heard that
OL,8,FLinehan had called Brooks a "sissy
OL,9,Fporn-watching scumbag," a "groomer"
OL,10,Fand a "disgusting incel," with the
OL,11,Fcomplainant responding: "You're the
OL,12,Fincel, you're divorced."
OL,14,FProsecutor, Julia Faure Walker, told
OL,15,Fthe court that Linehan had written
OL,16,F"repeated, abusive, unreasonable"
OL,17,Fsocial media posts about Brooks.
