OL,7,FThe 57-year-old Irish comedy writer
OL,8,Fwas arrested at Heathrow Airport after
OL,9,Fflying in from Arizona in September by
OL,10,Fthe Met Police on suspicion of
OL,11,Finciting violence over three posts he
OL,12,Fhad made on X.
OL,14,FThe arrest sparked controversy, with
OL,15,FConservative politicians and Harry
OL,16,FPotter author JK Rowling among those
OL,17,Fwho criticised the arrest.
